iled to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to charge card: could not charge the card: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: connect: connection refused\\\"`\n   - **Occurrence count**: 1\n\n3. **Log 3**\n   - **Service**: Paymentservice\n   - **Message**: `PluginLoader#load: Could not load plugin @opentelemetry/plugin-grpc-js of module @grpc/grpc-js. Error: Cannot find module '@opentelemetry/plugin-grpc-js'`\n   - **Occurrence count**: 1\n\n### 分析异常模式\n\n**提取的关键词**:\n- `connection refused`\n- `plugin`\n- `Cannot find module`\n- `transport`\n- `Error while dialing`\n\n### 初步假设\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"connection refused\", \"plugin\", \"Cannot find module\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"插件加载问题导致某些模块无法启动。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PluginLoader#load: could not load plugin @opentelemetry/plugin-http of module http.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"连接被拒绝，可能是由于目标服务（paymentservice）的网络配置问题。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n我们在这个初始扫描阶段中提取了若干关键错误，可能的根因包括插件加载问题和前端服务尝试连接 paymentservice 时的网络问题。在后续阶段中可以继续深入分析以确认根因。", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据 UUID 4e221a94-277 分析获取的调用链数据，已发现以下显著异常：\n\n### 延迟相关异常\n- **checkoutservice → emailservice**:\n  - 操作: `hipstershop.EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation`\n  - 正常耗时: `669 ms` → 异常耗时: `2073 ms`，延迟比 > 3\n- **checkoutservice → shippingservice**:\n  - 操作: `hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote`\n  - 正常耗时: `9.34 seconds` → 异常耗时: `51.57 seconds`，延迟比 > 5\n- **frontend → checkoutservice**:\n  - 操作: `hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder`\n  - 正常耗时: `144.33 seconds` → 异常耗时: `288.88 seconds`，延迟成倍增加。\n\n### 错误状态码\n显然与 HTTP `connection refused`